Hmm, Nobeard, you got what I was doing with metal colours, it's exactly what I was going for the thing you mentioned. He's been dead awhile, looks saturated, not shiny, but has regenerated abit since he's awake.<br>
<br>
The logo is the stamp they use to put in some episodes on the autobots and the stamp they use to put on the toys, especially the G1 series. I used the exact symbol from the Transformers font. <br>
<br>
His head is that way bcoz your'e looking up at him and his head placement on his torso is almost centered(not precisely), but still futher in.<br>
